  "text": [
    "Once we liked the conspicuous",
    "but constrained,",
    "the push-up bra",
    "under the shirt-waist,",
    "a small bow",
    "at the throat,",
    "the appearance",
    "of a struggle",
    "toward the diminutive,",
    "the punctum.",
    "\u2022",
    "The slender",
    "second hand",
    "jerking forward",
    "as if helpless,",
    "making its same sound.",
    "\u2022",
    "We might stand",
    "in a thicket",
    "where a battle had",
    "taken place",
    "and be thrilled",
    "by the far-off roar",
    "of traffic"
  ],
  "title": "Taking Place",
  "year": ""
}